data.description: Motivated Seller! Lots of room to grow your family in this cedar siding mobile home with metal roof (replaced 2015) located on 1.84 acres in Wakulla County.  Wood burning stone fireplace, spacious kitchen with island, and a split floor plan for privacy.  Septic tank last pumped Dec. of 2022, Water softener installed 2021, Refrigerator 2019 and Dishwasher 2023. Home is being sold "AS IS" with rights to inspect. USDA eligible. Home Warranty up to $525 is being offered with an accepted  contract. Camper and other items are in the process of being removed from the property.
